      },
      {
        "type": "instruction",
        "text": "Enter through the Trident Grand Mall parking and collect a parking ticket (free for the first hour).\n2GIS Entrance Guide"
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "url": "https://images.prismic.io/dbhq-deliveroo-riders-website/aOeVjp5xUNkB1yFI_IMG_6365.jpg?auto=format,compress&rect=0,0,4032,3024&w=1200&h=900"
      },
      {
        "type": "instruction",
        "text": "2. Drive or walk down to Basement Level 2 (B2)."
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "url": "https://images.prismic.io/dbhq-deliveroo-riders-website/aOehBJ5xUNkB1yK4_IMG_6366copy1.jpg?auto=format,compress&rect=0,1,6067,4029&w=1200&h=797"
      },
      {
        "type": "instruction",
        "text": "3. At the end of B2, look for the Deliveroo HOP signs and follow them to the order collection site."
      }
    ],
    "map_url": null,
    "directions_url": null
  },
  {
    "name": "Deliveroo Editions - Majestic Tower (Downtown)",
    "url": "https://riders.deliveroo.ae/en/news/deliveroo-editionsdowntownaccess",
    "phone": null,
    "floor": null,
    "unit": null,
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "image",
        "url": "https://images.prismic.io/dbhq-deliveroo-riders-website/aH3-nkMqNJQqIIzl_MajesticTower.png?auto=format,compress&rect=0,0,1280,587&w=1200&h=550"
      },
      {
        "type": "instruction",
        "text": "1. Park your bike in the Deliveroo motorbike parking inside Majestic Tower. 2GIS Entrance Guide"
      },
      {
        "type": "instruction",
        "text": "Note: Be careful of the parking barrier when entering and exiting"
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "url": "https://images.prismic.io/dbhq-deliveroo-riders-website/aH3_GUMqNJQqIIz7_WhatsAppImage2025-07-05at16.43.36-1-.jpeg?auto=format,compress&rect=0,0,1280,587&w=1200&h=550"
      },
      {
        "type": "instruction",
        "text": "2. Look for Deliveroo motorbike parking in the basement"
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "url": "https://images.prismic.io/dbhq-deliveroo-riders-website/aH3_jUMqNJQqII0Q_WhatsAppImage2025-07-05at16.43.36.jpeg?auto=format,compress&rect=0,0,1280,681&w=1200&h=638"
      },
      {
        "type": "instruction",
        "text": "In the center of the building in the basement parking, you’ll see a door to enter and go up the stairs to the ground floor."
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "url": "https://images.prismic.io/dbhq-deliveroo-riders-website/aH3_6kMqNJQqII0w_HOP-deliveroo-majestic.png?auto=format,compress&rect=0,0,1280,681&w=1200&h=638"
      },
      {
        "type": "instruction",
        "text": "4. Once at the ground floor level, access the Deliveroo Editions Downtown store from the canal-facing side of the building"
      }
    ],
    "map_url": null,
    "directions_url": null
  },
